				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Emulators that can run a wide variety of commercial NES games need to have accurate cycle counts for all instructions. Games' raster effect loops can and do depend on extra cycles inserted due to page crossing.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

